    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Cost: 4 Creation Points</p><p>Drain: 5 CCD Chakra</p><p></p><p>You augment your Genjutsu to throw off the equilibrium of the target creature. </p><p>On a failure or on a hit with a Genjutsu attack,, they become Deafened until the start of their next turn. </p><p>On a critical failure, they gain a rank of bleeding and become Deafened until the end of their next turn as their eardrums rupture. </p><p>If the Genjutsu would already deafen, the duration of the deafen is doubled.</p>",
